 combination of 欠勤 \'\'kekkin\'\' (not showing up for work) and \'\'king\'\'.\n\n==In other languages==\n{{Other languages|type=Normal|type2=Normal\n|ja=ケッキング \'\'Kekking\'\'|jameaning=From {{tt|欠勤 \'\'kekkin\'\'|absence}} and \'\'king\'\'\n|fr=Monaflèmit|frmeaning=From \'\'monarch\'\' and {{tt|\'\'flemme\'\'|slacking off}}\n|es=Slaking|esmeaning=Same as English name\n|de=Letarking|demeaning=From {{tt|\'\'lethargisch\'\'|lethargic}} and \'\'king\'\'\n|it=Slaking|itmeaning=Same as English name\n|ko=게을킹 \'\'Geulking\'\'|komeaning=From {{tt|게으르다 \'\'ge\'eureuda\'\'|to be lazy}} and \'\'king\'\'\n|zh_cmn=請假王 / 请假王 \'\'Qǐngjiàwáng\'\'|zh_cmnmeaning=From {{tt|請假 \'\'qǐngjià\'\'|to request for a leave of absence}} and {{tt|王 \'\'wáng\'\'|king}}\n|ru=Слакинг \'\'Slaking\'\'|rumeaning=Transcription of English name\n}}\n<br clear="left">\n\n==Related articles==\n* [[Norman\'s Slaking]]\n\n==External links==\n\n{{-}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Head|type=Normal}}\n{{PokémonPrevNext/Pokémon|type=Normal|prevnum=288|prev=Vigoroth|nextnum=290|next=Nincada}}\n|}\n{{Project Pokédex notice}}\n\n[[de:Letarking]]\n[[es:Slaking]]\n[[fr:Monaflèmit]]\n[[it:Slaking]]\n[[ja:ケッキング]]\n[[zh:请假王]]'}